title: Introducing: High Low With EmRata
description:
High Low with EmRata is a brand-new chat series where she’ll be talking everything from politics, philosophy, and feminism, to sex, gossip, and TikTok.
Every Tuesday, she'll host intimate conversations with special guests, including celebs, incredible authors, close friends, and people she admires. In the week’s second episode, she'll talk about whatever’s happening in the world and what it’s making her think about, including anecdotes, personal opinions and, ideally, some thought provoking questions. Finally, you can subscribe to a third exclusive episode each week where you get to be part of the show. She'll go through your comments and answer your DMs.
From Sony Music Entertainment, Somethin’ Else, and Bitch Era Media production, listen and follow High Low With EmRata wherever you get your podcasts.
https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/high-low-with-emrata/id1648732468
https://open.spotify.com/show/1sbjTlSAwpfTXjyDTr3yYg
